"72:12:2" : {s: 72, a: 12, w: 2, r: "ظنن", t: "ظَنَنَّآ", l: "ظَنَّ", lc: 47, tl: "ẓanannā", lb: "মনে করা, ভাবা, ধারণা/ অনুমান করা",e: "[we] have become certain", b: "মনে করেছিলাম", i: "kami menyangka/yakin", f: 2, rm: "To think, suppose, doubt, assume, deem, believe, know, imagine, suspect, conjunctive, be sure of something in view of ones observations. As a general rule often this verb is succeeded by anna or an, that means to be sure about.", ag: "فعل ماض وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "1", gen: "", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "ظَنَّ،ظَنُّ"},
